{
  "stem": "21437.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she was-- I didn't see her after the war at all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't-- no, I didn't see her even in Peterswaldau.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "A couple of them were taken away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were unprotect-- the weather.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, we, we were still-- we sort of had an occasional shelter.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We worked inside, and we worked outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They went outside for the whole day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, people were coming into the camp-- like those Dutch people were coming into the camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Again, you see, I mean-- when I talk about it, I, I can visualize-- I can literally taste this-- we were disoriented at times.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We did not look.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know the next second.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, in retrospect, I can see it, sort of, you know, in a neater way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I can remember it-- I can remember it visually.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can remember it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can visualize it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But at the time, I didn't really know how much I'm taking in or how much I am not.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I am only taking-- telling you about this what I took in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The rest what happened, I don't really know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So you spent, about, as you said, about a year in Oderberg.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then you said the camp was liquidated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What happened, and how did you get--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went into-- we just-- we were just rounded up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had whatever couple of things, and we were taken.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The men and the girls were taken to Seibersdorf.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "S-E-I-B-E-R-S-D-O-R-F.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is when we already then-- the seven girls kept in touch, but we were already-- there was an influx, you know, from other camps.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we went to work there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went to some little factory or whatever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't-- whatever presented itself.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
